Accessing  the specific property: 

  1. Dot Notation.

    Syntax:
        var val= objName . keyname; 

  2. Square Bracket Notation:

    Syntax:

        var val= objName[" keyName"]  
----------------------------------------

Adding New Property into Object:
    
  

        objname["keyname"]= value;

        objname.keyname = value;
