--------------------

        syntax:
        --------

        objname.keyname = "newvalue"

        objname["keyname"] = "newvalue"

        Ex:  obj1.place = "NLR";

             obj1["place"] = "NLR"

Deleting the property:
---------------------

        syntax:

        delete objname.keyname;

